data.description: Explore the POTENTIAL at 724 Maplewood Ave, a RARE GEM located in Ambridge, PA. This home features FIVE GENEROUS BEDROOMS and a VERSATILE ROOM on the first floor, PRIMED to become its SIXTH. Offering MULTIFACETED OPTIONS for INVESTORS OF ALL KINDS, it boasts THREE FULL BATHROOMS—one on EACH FLOOR. Including OFF-STREET PARKING, a DETACHED GARAGE, a FENCED-IN BACKYARD, a NEWER ROOF, and a NEWER HOT WATER TANK, makes this an IRRESISTIBLE OPPORTUNITY for ANYONE.
